AUDIO: 'Claude Code can now do in a matter of hours and minutes what used to take developers entire weeks, but only if you actually know how to use the tool to get the outputs you\'re looking for. In this video, we\'re going to run through 30 key concepts to help get you the most out of Claude Code and how to actually use it'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'day-to-day. But first, what is Claude Code and how does it differ from the normal chat interfaces that we tend to use with Gemini, OpenAI, and Claude itself? Well, think the chat interfaces'

[00:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'as literally just inputs and outputs for conversation or threads. Yes, they can take some action, but it\'s a bit more limited, maybe creating a Word doc or updating some, for example, Notion templates, anything like this, but it'

[00:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'can\'t really build anything or go beyond that. That\'s where Claude Code comes into play. We\'re able to go through and create our very own applications, websites, and much, much more because Claude Code will literally help us write'

