[14:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'it will read your entire code base and project that you\'ve got set up and create a brand new version. We\'ll run this in the background. Of course, we\'ve got nothing set up at the moment, so it should go through and just create an empty one on the left-hand side here. Or'

[14:52] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'you\'re all also to go through and generate it manually, and we just do the plus button here, and then we just type claude.md, which will create that markdown document for us to go through and add all of the'

