[18:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'claude-verbose, and this will basically ask Claude to go into lots of details for the output that you\'re trying to get. Next up, we\'ve got skills. These are pre-written instructions that we\'re able to give to'

[18:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Claude to execute a specific process or retrieve an output that we\'re looking for. We\'re able to store it in what\'s called a skill.md file. An MD file is just pure text that we\'re able to use to'

[18:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'store all of this information. I\'ll show you an example in a second, but just to run through the entire structure. We\'re going to give our skill a specific name. We also need to give it a description of'

[18:51] [scene:talk]
